value.string: House with detached ohana across the street from park and close to the Golf Course. May be non-conforming issues but a great opportunity for large extended family.

One of the few properties in Waiehu Terrace that has a huge yard. Conveniently located near schools, grocery stores, churches, parks, public facilities and minutes away from the beach! Property is occupied and occupants are not to be disturbed or contacted under any circumstances. Interior inspections are not available and property is being sold as is. Expertly constructed contemporary residence in Pineapple Hill Estates, Kapalua with almost 6,000 sq.ft under roof perched on almost 1/2 acre overlooking lush vistas of Napili, Mauna Kahalawai, unobstructed ocean, sunset, Molokai and Lanai island views. Single level living affords comfort and bliss for intimate groups in a serene and private setting. Feel the quintessential awe moment right as you enter the the front door- your eyes are dawn outward through the great room and the large slider doors to the pool, spa, and the impressive panoramic views. An expansive floor plan that transitions nicely from the open kitchen to the dining area and into the great room. The master suite is set apart from the rest of the rooms in its own wing with two lanais, one private, and one opening up to the pool and outdoor shower, both with stunning ocean views. On the opposite wing of the home, each guest suite has a private lanai and expansive ocean and mountain views. Soffitt ceilings and mahogany crown molding in all suites and the great room. The sliding doors and large windows invite the crisp and comfortable breezes, natural light, and stunning outdoor setting into the home. Envision stainless thermadore appliances, rough cut travertine, exotic hardwoods, granite, and custom touches inside and out. Come live you Hawaii Life at 223 Crestiview as this fully furnished executive home awaits you.
